pandangan pertama.

50
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:47,980
Merindukannya selama
sepuluh ribu tahun.

51
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:50,510
Serius?

52
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:53,900
Serius.

53
