63
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:16,230
Bersedia, tentu saja bersedia.

64
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,420
Sepengetahuanku,

65
00:04:17,780 --> 00:04:19,420
Siluman Bulan Ungu pada jam ini
setiap harinya

66
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:21,310
selalu mandi di Mata Air Bulan Ungu.

67
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:22,230
Jika kau pergi sekarang,

68
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:23,260
