108
00:06:55,030 --> 00:06:57,470
Kalau begitu, Jing Jian akan
mewakili adikku menerima hukuman.

109
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,980
Segalanya dijalankan sesuai
peraturan suku Siluman.

110
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:07,470
Di surat kau bilang,

111
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:10,310
asalkan Ayahanda mengeluarkan
Cambuk Giok Ungu untuk membantu,

112
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:12,790
