154
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:01,150
Jing Jian undur diri dulu.

155
00:09:18,660 --> 00:09:20,350
Hou Chi kenapa masih belum kembali?

156
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:23,030
Tabib Bei Chi, apakah kau di dalam?

157
00:09:23,420 --> 00:09:24,150
Siapa yang di luar?

158
