Jika orang Suku Siluman
mengetahui identitasnya,

185
00:11:02,740 --> 00:11:03,820
takutnya dia akan dalam bahaya.

186
00:11:04,350 --> 00:11:05,740
Penjagaan Istana Xuanjing sangat ketat.

187
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:07,620
Walaupun kita berdua menerobos
masuk ke istana,

188
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:08,990
