00:13:31,470 --> 00:13:32,380
Kau sepertinya minum terlalu banyak.

225
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:33,230
Kau salah orang.

226
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:34,430
Aku adalah Hou Chi,

227
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:35,670
bukan Shang Gu apa itu.

228
00:13:36,590 --> 00:13:37,260
Jelas-jelas kau orangnya.

229
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:38,700
Lepaskan aku!

230
00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:40,060
Lepaskan!

231
00:13:43,470 --> 00:13:44,030
Shang Gu!

